These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, may, june, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| Birthday   | june  | september      | august   | january     | may    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, snooker, whist, poker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, surfing, swimming, tennis
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person playing snooker and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Game   | snooker     | whist       | poker    | canasta | scrabble   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | badminton | swimming | tennis      | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, poppy, iris, sunflower
1. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
6. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks | filmmaking | reading    | video-games |
| Flower   | iris     | tulip        | poppy      | orchid | sunflower      |

