.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, indian, russian, malaysian, turkish
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, satire, scientific, spy
1. the russian is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the turkish is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the indian is between the person watching satire movies and the turkish##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Nationality         | canadian      | malaysian | russian | indian   | turkish  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy    | satire        | adventure | martial-arts |

