.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, cricket, tennis, ice-hockey
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | tea      | lemonade | iced-tea   | soy-milk  | mirinda  |
| Sport   | cricket | tennis | volleyball | rugby | ice-hockey |

