.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, october, november, january, december
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, engineer, paramedic, security-guard, software-developer
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
2. the engineer is between the software-developer and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the paramedic is in an even position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Birthday   | october        | august                | january  | november  | december            |
| Job        | electrician | software-developer | engineer | paramedic | security-guard |

