.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, tram, train, bike
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
9. the person driving the train is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage   | water       | milk   | lemonade    | sprite    | hot-chocolate |
| Transport        | tram | motorbike | taxi | bike | train     |

