.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, gardening, baking, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, musical, mystery, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Hobby      | gardening  | rock-climbing       | filmmaking      | baking  | writing   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts | scientific | musical | mystery |

