.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There 5 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, radish, lime, grapefruit
5 different pets are kept: fish, goat, guinea-pig, horse, pony
1. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
2. the person eating lime is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
5. the person eating broccoli is the owner of the fish##1
6. the person eating radish is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating pepper##2
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating radish##1
8. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Food   | grapefruit | broccoli | radish     | pepper | lime |
| Pet           | goat | fish     | guinea-pig | pony    | horse      |

