2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking water is the person eating pepper##1
