.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, bluemaster, swisher, dunhill
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the trike is the game-smoker##1
3. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the trike and the aristoff-smoker##2
7. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar        | swisher | dunhill | game  | bluemaster | aristoff     |
| Transport   | bus  | car     | trike | boat      | skateboard |

