4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
7. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the horse and the person eating cabbage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | raspberry   | pepper  | cabbage     | artichoke | grapefruit |
