.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
5 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly
There are 5 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, colombian, turkish
1. the american is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the american is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the british is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
7. the chinese is in an odd position##4
8. the colombian is in the middle##1
9. the british is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Game   | canasta  | mah-jongg    | bridge | scrabble   | monopoly |
| Nationality   | turkish | british | colombian    | american | chinese |

