5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
