.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, satire, scientific, zombie
5 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, fish, guinea-pig, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts | zombie     | satire | scientific |
| Pet     | guinea-pig       | chinchilla   | fish | snake   | goldfish        |

