.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
City: edinburgh, marseilles, prague, paris, miami
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, italian, nigerian, thai
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
2. the italian is the italian##1
3. the nigerian is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
5. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the thai##2
6. the dutch is between the person traveling to paris and the thai##2
7. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
8. the thai is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| City         | paris | prague | marseilles | miami | edinburgh     |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | dutch   | thai       | italian | australian |

