.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, comedy, spy, action
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | comedy      | spy | action     | satire      |
| Transport     | train | quad-bike | taxi | airplane | snowmobile |

 